Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.24,0:00:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是银之战舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.08,0:00:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.78,0:00:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变更作战计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.06,0:01:03.29,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,just keep on trying, keep on flying\N{\c&HFFBF00&}just keep on trying, keep on flying
