Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.31,0:01:25.84,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,与你的烟云时代交响曲\N{\c&HFFBF00&}君とのCloud Age Symphony
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.92,0:01:35.22,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,飞向云海的彼端　飞往光芒照射的方向\N{\c&HFFBF00&}雲の海の向こうに　光が射す方へ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.83,0:01:50.19,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah～是否可以遇见有如魔法的那一刻？\N{\c&HFFBF00&}Ah～魔法のような一瞬に会えるのか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.27,0:01:57.48,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,取代寒冷的黑夜\N{\c&HFFBF00&}冷たい夜を引き替えに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.55,0:02:04.58,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我俩展翅飞翔\N{\c&HFFBF00&}二人は羽ばたいて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.65,0:02:15.53,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在那尽头  抓住了永恒…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}永远を掴む、その果てには
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.07,0:02:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}戴芬妮女王\NQueen Delphine
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.73,0:02:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副舰长，舰长他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.23,0:02:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.76,0:02:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且迪奥和艾儿…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.20,0:02:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有克劳士他们\N都被那位总帅给带走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.24,0:02:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士也被带走了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.07,0:03:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要带走克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.72,0:03:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.16,0:03:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.03,0:03:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.70,0:03:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得呢，鲁修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.57,0:03:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜您了，戴芬妮陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.30,0:03:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.77,0:03:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.81,0:03:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥他怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.25,0:03:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道迪奥他\N为什么那么怕你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.88,0:03:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你打算抹杀迪奥他的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.95,0:03:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.35,0:03:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们感情可好的很呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.56,0:03:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁修拉你都不在乎吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.97,0:04:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.94,0:04:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这世界是属于我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.27,0:04:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们也来帮他庆祝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.84,0:04:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥今天就要变大人了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.26,0:04:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总帅万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.53,0:04:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总帅万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.27,0:04:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫做克劳士是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.34,0:04:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很想知道\N这片天空发生了什么事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.28,0:04:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我的话，就可以告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.12,0:04:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天空是属于我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.49,0:04:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道我在做些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.35,0:04:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就等于知道了\N你所想知道的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.19,0:04:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宣誓仪式开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.29,0:05:01.92,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,我心与天空同在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.00,0:05:04.33,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,与白云共存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.40,0:05:06.42,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,蓝天解放了我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.50,0:05:09.40,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,尊荣的铜墙铁壁\N守护我们免于地上炼火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.47,0:05:12.17,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,我们愿献身给天上的风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.24,0:05:14.71,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,直到攸久之时光尽头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.78,0:05:16.90,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,在蓝天白云
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.98,0:05:18.88,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,与红墙的环绕里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.95,0:05:20.61,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,我们将守卫祖国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.68,0:05:22.88,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,我们与天空同在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.39,0:05:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.65,0:05:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脸上刻有宣誓印记的\N未来领袖们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.59,0:05:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一个世代的基尔特\N将由你们来打造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.46,0:05:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基尔特是法律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.33,0:05:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基尔特是秩序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.37,0:05:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基尔特就是世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.77,0:05:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追求的是永恒的安宁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.91,0:05:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请赐予世界永恒的安宁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.21,0:05:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚给忠诚的奖励将很特别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.81,0:05:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一代的基尔特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.92,0:06:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宣誓之剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.76,0:06:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有为基尔特带来永恒的人\N才能够拥有这把剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.66,0:06:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若想继承我的名号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.66,0:06:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就拿起这把宣誓之剑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.97,0:06:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后胜利的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.17,0:06:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将赐予这总帅的头衔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.80,0:06:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑只有一把
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.67,0:06:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你们以灵魂来宣誓的人数呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.15,0:06:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们明白了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.91,0:06:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是今晚成人仪式的考验
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.92,0:06:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来，这就开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.06,0:06:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.06,0:06:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算叫他做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.93,0:06:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是迪奥他姊姊吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.33,0:06:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快阻止他啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.37,0:06:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我偏不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.42,0:07:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了，迪奥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.35,0:07:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是在天空所发生的事\N克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.69,0:07:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基尔特宣誓仪式的时间到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.73,0:07:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全军准备进攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.90,0:07:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备进攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.24,0:07:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.27,0:07:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，这是朋友给我的生还章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.81,0:07:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可是手制的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.94,0:07:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.04,0:07:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.74,0:07:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果集满了20枚生还章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.88,0:07:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以升级\N并选择自己喜欢的船舰搭乘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.98,0:07:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.98,0:07:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.39,0:07:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.79,0:07:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在拿到这次作战的\N第20枚生还章之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.02,0:07:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就好比是我的护身符一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.97,0:07:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是他朋友的话\N就好好看清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.77,0:08:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看迪奥他有多美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.05,0:08:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿，怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.82,0:08:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴芬妮陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.35,0:08:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是巨茧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.92,0:08:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿．薇丝，接下来的主角是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.09,0:08:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快过来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.06,0:08:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，迪奥呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.53,0:08:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要知道结果就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.43,0:08:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是万一他死了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.80,0:08:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是他自己不对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.54,0:08:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想知道\N是谁会继承我的名号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.21,0:08:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士，快带艾儿．薇丝过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.41,0:08:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.48,0:08:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我戴芬妮叫你带她过来\N你就给我带过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.90,0:09:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.77,0:09:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是苦了你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.44,0:09:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帅哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.64,0:09:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.45,0:09:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.68,0:09:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙偏偏就这种时候不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.59,0:09:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去接克劳士回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.82,0:09:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顺便到基尔特逛逛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.39,0:09:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你都没听说吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.86,0:09:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在起要杀进基尔特呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.53,0:09:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦被砍就要砍回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.43,0:09:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是杀无赦银之战舰的规矩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.40,0:09:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且还要砍它个三倍才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.14,0:09:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可怕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.51,0:09:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊萨，还不快把装备拿来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.31,0:09:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，我这就去拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.65,0:09:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇把先锋艇修好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.72,0:09:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.22,0:09:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.69,0:09:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.29,0:09:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这在哪里找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.19,0:10:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看它被丢在休息室里\N就把它拿来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.20,0:10:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这画的是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.87,0:10:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿说是她梦到的风景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.27,0:10:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.57,0:10:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要去把\N克劳士和艾儿救回来才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.17,0:10:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都画到这个地步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.48,0:10:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总该让人家好好画完吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.41,0:10:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然都已经修好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.81,0:10:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干脆就驾着克劳士的先锋艇\N给它杀过去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.78,0:10:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要说蠢话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.45,0:10:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.89,0:10:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士和拉薇的先锋艇\N并不是战斗机好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.90,0:10:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.43,0:10:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.33,0:10:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.71,0:10:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望不会发生流血事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.87,0:10:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把枪藏起来，快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.64,0:10:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对哦，不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.74,0:11:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.01,0:11:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那艘船上也有船员不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.04,0:11:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们很幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.98,0:11:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能够为了我\N而死在EXILE的触手下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.15,0:11:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.16,0:11:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道了吧，EXILE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.93,0:11:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错，你的钥匙就在这里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.63,0:11:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.03,0:11:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说艾儿．薇丝啊\N你知道EXILE是什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.31,0:11:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有知道的权利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.08,0:11:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.48,0:12:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你给我安静点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.15,0:12:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿．薇丝，让我来告诉你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.12,0:12:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE其实就是\N很久以前的移民船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,移民船？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.33,0:12:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.39,0:12:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是创造了这个世界的人们\N当初所搭乘的船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.56,0:12:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要坐上了这个\N就可以前往别的世界了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.97,0:12:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谣言这东西还真可怕呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.74,0:12:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银之战舰不也是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.77,0:12:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么杀无赦的银之战舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.51,0:12:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么EXILE是最终兵器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.71,0:12:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎哟，真可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.28,0:12:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把人家说成杀人毁灭的道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.95,0:12:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是不是显示出地上的人\N想要毁灭这个世界的愿望啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.95,0:12:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要好好珍惜愿望才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.72,0:12:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这才有梦想嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.59,0:12:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正因为有梦\N地上的人们才会辛劳工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.53,0:12:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此，让大家继续做梦\N就是我的义务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.67,0:12:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直漂流在大风暴区的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.70,0:12:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该还是由我来掌管不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.01,0:13:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不能随便让别人给看见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.76,0:13:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿．薇丝，你过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.92,0:13:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，不要过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.63,0:13:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.13,0:13:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在…这里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.87,0:13:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE，你看清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.07,0:14:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你从漫长的睡眠里\N唤醒的钥匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.91,0:14:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.24,0:14:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可爱的艾儿．薇丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.31,0:14:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始主角就是你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.38,0:14:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希卡达，把诗人带来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.09,0:14:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,属下遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.02,0:14:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诗人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.37,0:14:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.08,0:14:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.01,0:14:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.58,0:14:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在要让你看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.55,0:14:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是在这片天空所发生的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.79,0:14:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是在这片天空里\N即将要发生的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.41,0:15:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诗人先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.74,0:15:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你藏着的言灵告诉我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.41,0:15:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你再抗拒也没有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.55,0:15:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的心已经被这花刺所带的\N真实的血清给侵蚀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.90,0:15:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当初你们驾着这架先锋艇\N来到银之战舰上时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.43,0:15:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长曾经这么跟我说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.54,0:15:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说你们很像以前的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.81,0:15:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得克劳士他飞在一个\N比我们还要更高的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.25,0:15:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.18,0:15:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不能没有他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他那人虽然顽固
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.32,0:16:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但对我和周遭的人\N其实算是满体贴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.29,0:16:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.46,0:16:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一下子不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.80,0:16:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我…感觉一蹶不振
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.23,0:16:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不晓得该怎么振作起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.41,0:16:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜，艾丽丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.11,0:16:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你们救救克劳士，救救艾儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.68,0:16:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们答应你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.25,0:16:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定会把他们救出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.95,0:16:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诗人先生，来为我念首诗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.42,0:16:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,念那首远古时代的觉醒之诗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.89,0:16:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧，亚力克斯．罗威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.13,0:16:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里为我说出关键谜诗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.14,0:16:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先是达格贝家的谜诗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.08,0:17:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把大地染成金色的波浪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.88,0:17:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抚育生命万物之气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.65,0:17:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小麦之…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.46,0:17:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.24,0:17:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巨茧产生反应了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.54,0:17:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真傻，亚力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.88,0:17:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果打一开始你老老实实念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.35,0:17:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不用受这种罪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.55,0:17:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己不好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.68,0:17:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁修拉！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.02,0:17:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁修拉乖孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.09,0:17:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以帮我看着你的朋友别动吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.16,0:17:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不希望有太多杂音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.90,0:17:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,属下遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.17,0:17:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧，亚力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.24,0:17:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次换汉弥尔敦家的谜诗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.37,0:18:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在记忆的彼方…存在的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.28,0:18:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切诞生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.42,0:18:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切回归的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.99,0:18:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色的…星球…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.81,0:18:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发现身分不明的音源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.24,0:18:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是动力音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.88,0:18:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该是刚才那道光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.31,0:18:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.85,0:18:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巨茧的雷射扫描似乎是结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.32,0:18:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚力克斯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.15,0:18:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经被戴芬妮攻陷了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.73,0:19:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，接着念巴席安努家的谜诗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.24,0:19:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.44,0:19:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.18,0:19:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不可能不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.45,0:19:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该已经拿到所有的谜诗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.72,0:19:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.26,0:19:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.86,0:19:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不可能违抗得了\N真实的血清的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.97,0:19:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴芬妮陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.17,0:19:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个男人或许真的不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.64,0:19:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.61,0:19:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.61,0:19:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你这样就瞒得过我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.78,0:19:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还真可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.52,0:19:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.89,0:19:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.16,0:19:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.46,0:20:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你身边应该有人知道\N巴席安努家的谜诗才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.00,0:20:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.78,0:20:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个乖孩子，亚力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.09,0:20:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希达卡，把皇帝带到这里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.96,0:20:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,属下遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.34,0:20:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.61,0:20:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来今天的关键谜诗\N只能念到这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.51,0:20:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次再继续吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.48,0:20:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手，你不要碰艾儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.02,0:20:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴芬妮陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.55,0:20:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宣誓仪式的典礼会场\N有连络进来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.12,0:21:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，结束了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.86,0:21:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥，你成为大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.83,0:21:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继承总帅头衔的是迪奥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.13,0:21:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我俩一同来继承\N艾拉克莱家的秘技吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.14,0:21:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我们回去为迪奥庆祝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.84,0:21:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁修拉，把艾儿．薇丝带走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.51,0:22:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.35,0:22:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那边那位朋友也一起带走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.12,0:22:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精彩的还在后头呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.62,0:22:39.78,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜的时光逐渐逼近\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜の時間が迫り来る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.39,0:22:46.45,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你离我如此接近感觉  却好远…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたはこんな近く  でも遠い…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.53,0:22:57.60,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你的憧憬是什么  心中想的又是誰\N{\c&HFFBF00&}何に憧れて だれを想うのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.67,0:23:03.20,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你舍命奋斗的身影\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いのち賭ける姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.28,0:23:11.98,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,有一种透明的美丽  令我不禁哑口无言\N{\c&HFFBF00&}透き通る美しさに 言葉を飲んだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.06,0:23:17.93,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你欲飞往天际\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたが空を行くなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.99,0:23:23.73,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我愿成为你的翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}わたしは翼になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.80,0:23:29.60,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,无论风有多么强\N{\c&HFFBF00&}どんなに強い風にも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.67,0:23:35.37,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,也永远不会折断的柔婉翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}けして折れない しなやかな羽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.45,0:23:47.41,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,相信有一天  我会拥有那样一对翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いつか　きっと持つから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.99,0:23:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（下回预告）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.99,0:23:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥身体里那个坏孩子\N已经不在了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.60,0:23:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.53,0:23:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢听话的迪奥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.20,0:24:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为我可爱的迪奥\N带来了奖品送你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.10,0:24:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.51,0:24:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮他取个名字吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.11,0:24:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一回，最后流亡 第23话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.88,0:24:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骑士鲁修拉\NCastling Lucciola
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.98,0:24:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.25,0:24:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从今天起你的名字就叫鲁修拉
